text: Ruby Rose Langenheim (born 20 March 1986) is an Australian model, actress, and television presenter. She is known for her role as Stella in Orange Is the New Black. She also starred in action movies Resident Evil: The Final Chapter (2016), XXX: Return of Xander Cage (2017) and John Wick: Chapter 2 (2017) and has co-starred in the musical comedy Pitch Perfect 3 (2017) and the monster movie The Meg (2018). In August 2018, Rose had been cast as Batwoman in the upcoming Arrowverse crossover and in the television series of the same name.
